TY  - JOUR
TI  - Coherency Conditions in Simultaneous Linear Equation Models with Endogenous Switching Regimes
AU  - Gourieroux, C.
AU  - Laffont, J. J.
AU  - Monfort, A.
AB  - [In this paper we consider the problem of the existence of a well-defined reduced form in the context of piecewise linear models. We give a general theorem which provides necessary and sufficient conditions, called coherency conditions, for such an existence. This result is applied to various kinds of models: self-selectivity models, simultaneous equation probit and tobit models, multimarkets disequilibrium models.]
C1  - Full publication date: Apr., 1980
