TY  - JOUR
TI  - Testing for Serial Correlation in Simultaneous Equation Models
AU  - Harvey, A. C.
AU  - Phillips, G. D. A.
AB  - [This paper presents the theoretical development of bounds tests and exact tests for serial correlation in the context of a simultaneous equation model which are analogous to those developed for single equation models. The powers of the exact tests are estimated and compared using Monte Carlo simulation of a three equation model.]
